#### Description

This dashboard provides comprehensive visibility into asset distribution within the Nozomi Networks platform using the Assets data stream.

It shows metrics for IT, OT, and IoT assets by technology category and name. High-risk assets (risk ≥ 40) are highlighted by type and vendor. The dashboard also includes asset distribution by OS, vendor, zone, and protocol. A saved search displays essential asset details to support monitoring and investigation.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/nozomi_networks/overview)**
